{"tid":2282810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓聯社：習近平正尋求訪韓 修補因薩德導彈系統疏遠的邦交關係","createTime":"2020-11-12T06:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T06:38:02.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d549aaec622cbad17bff55f093b88ddeacff94","tid":2282810,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"韓聯社稱中方正推進習近平最快本月底訪韓<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社引述消息透露，北京政府正推進國家主席習近平，在今個月底或下月中旬訪問南韓。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，如果習近平訪韓成行，兩國有望修復因為薩德導彈系統問題疏遠的關係，並就深化經貿合作、朝鮮半島核問題等交換意見。不過，美國總統特朗普對大選結果不滿、以及新型肺炎疫情，仍然是影響習近平能否訪韓的最大變數。<br />\n<br />\n報道又說，中共中央政治局委員楊潔篪在今年8月訪韓時表示，中方對推進習近平訪韓的態度已經相當積極。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559615-20201112.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559615-20201112.htm&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=ac4c4231\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559615-20201112.htm&h=94603ade\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559615-20201112.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6fe1f87fe4f135833314aa337958103156d60698","tid":2282810,"uid":30215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"起飛前先提交72小時陰性檢測報告，到達首爾機場再做個快速測試，陰性先放行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓仔敢唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e127a301821eef976b7f4f88caade1883ee1839","tid":2282810,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T06:38:02.000Z","msg":"拜登鴿派概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}